[Lee exhales deeply]

1:49:14.156 --> 1:49:15.461
[Lee sniffles]

1:49:17.028 --> 1:49:18.726
[Lee crying]

1:49:51.672 --> 1:49:53.108
[Maren] Where do we go next?

1:49:54.283 --> 1:49:55.240
[Lee] Anywhere.

1:49:56.241 --> 1:49:57.939
[Maren] Let's drive back.

1:49:57.982 --> 1:49:59.723
Until the truck
gives out somewhere.

1:50:00.985 --> 1:50:03.509
And then just stay.

1:50:04.380 --> 1:50:07.035
We can get a place, jobs.

1:50:07.949 --> 1:50:09.994
You know, like people do.

1:50:10.038 --> 1:50:13.084
[Lee] You wanna be people?
Let's be people.

1:50:13.128 --> 1:50:15.870
[Maren] Yeah.
Let's be them for a while.

1:50:21.919 --> 1:50:23.138
[Lee] Yeah,
we're in Ann Arbor now.

1:50:24.008 --> 1:50:25.270
Ann Arbor.

1:50:25.314 --> 1:50:26.707
Maren got a job
at the university,

1:50:26.750 --> 1:50:29.187
at the bookstore,
so, we're right near campus.

1:50:33.757 --> 1:50:34.715
What'd you say?

1:50:37.326 --> 1:50:38.806
Yeah, maybe if
we're here long enough.

1:50:38.849 --> 1:50:40.024
Hey, Kayla says hi.

1:50:41.025 --> 1:50:42.636
-Hi.
-Maren says hi.

1:50:42.679 --> 1:50:44.463
-She wants to come up.
-Yeah.

1:50:46.161 --> 1:50:47.902
[indistinct chatter]

1:51:21.979 --> 1:51:23.502
[indistinct chatter]

1:51:29.595 --> 1:51:32.207
Lee, I brought your...

1:51:35.166 --> 1:51:36.124
[sighs]

1:52:04.718 --> 1:52:06.023
[breathes deeply]

1:52:10.071 --> 1:52:12.508
-[Maren whimpering]
-[shushing]

1:52:20.995 --> 1:52:22.692
[Sully breathing heavily]

1:52:22.736 --> 1:52:24.955
I'm gonna take my hand away,

1:52:26.217 --> 1:52:27.784
and you're not gonna scream.

1:52:28.785 --> 1:52:30.656
Because Sully's a friend

1:52:31.701 --> 1:52:34.051
and we don't scream
at friends.

1:52:38.099 --> 1:52:39.361
[gasping]

1:52:46.020 --> 1:52:48.674
Where's your...
Where's your cutie-pie?

1:52:48.718 --> 1:52:50.024
[laughing]

1:52:50.807 --> 1:52:52.853
I saw him.

1:52:52.896 --> 1:52:56.770
I saw him walk out of here
half an hour ago.

1:52:58.859 --> 1:52:59.773
I don't know.

1:53:03.385 --> 1:53:05.169
What's all this for, Sully?

1:53:10.044 --> 1:53:11.306
Ever...

1:53:11.349 --> 1:53:14.439
Ever since I drove away
from you,

1:53:15.310 --> 1:53:17.268
up there in Minnesota,

1:53:18.879 --> 1:53:20.489
nothing's felt right.

1:53:23.448 --> 1:53:24.928
[Maren] What does that mean?

1:53:28.497 --> 1:53:29.454
[smacks lips]

1:53:29.890 --> 1:53:31.152
It means...

1:53:35.721 --> 1:53:37.811
[breathes heavily]

1:53:37.854 --> 1:53:38.855
It means...

1:53:41.379 --> 1:53:43.120
It mean... It...

1:53:43.164 --> 1:53:47.255
It means unfinished business.

1:53:53.130 --> 1:53:55.829
Sully, me and Lee...

1:53:59.745 --> 1:54:00.703
we are together now.

1:54:01.312 --> 1:54:02.661
[Maren gasps]

1:54:02.705 --> 1:54:05.186
That's not the business
I'm talkin' about.

1:54:13.759 --> 1:54:15.849
I don't mind.

1:54:15.892 --> 1:54:19.200
I don't... I don't mind
if you don't like Sully.

1:54:21.376 --> 1:54:26.511
What I mind is how much
you know about him

1:54:26.555 --> 1:54:28.600
in that little head of yours.

1:54:30.298 --> 1:54:32.691
You don't think
I'd tell anyone, right?

1:54:32.735 --> 1:54:34.780
[Sully groans]

1:54:34.824 --> 1:54:36.695
I mean, who would believe me?

1:54:36.739 --> 1:54:37.827
[Sully groans]

1:54:40.177 --> 1:54:44.268
And you're the one who told me
you don't kill any...

1:54:45.661 --> 1:54:47.619
You don't kill, right?

1:54:47.663 --> 1:54:48.882
You told me that, Sully.

1:54:48.925 --> 1:54:50.492
You know, I told...

1:54:50.535 --> 1:54:54.322
I used to try and tell people
the truth, you know.

1:54:57.673 --> 1:54:59.544
They never took me serious.

1:55:02.547 --> 1:55:03.722
[Sully sighs]

1:55:08.205 --> 1:55:10.468
I just wanted to be...

1:55:10.512 --> 1:55:13.602
I just wanted to be with
someone who understood.

1:55:14.429 --> 1:55:15.647
Do you know what I mean?

1:55:18.563 --> 1:55:19.477
Do you?

1:55:20.478 --> 1:55:21.392
Mm.

1:55:22.828 --> 1:55:23.829
Mm.

1:55:24.395 --> 1:55:25.919
[sniffling]

1:55:26.876 --> 1:55:27.833
Hmm.

1:55:31.359 --> 1:55:32.447
[Sully grunts softly]

1:55:33.491 --> 1:55:34.753
[door opens quietly]

1:55:42.892 --> 1:55:43.893
[Maren] Hey.

1:55:44.807 --> 1:55:46.765
You never get sick
of yourself?

1:55:54.556 --> 1:55:57.037
Sully just wants
to sleep at night.

1:55:57.863 --> 1:55:58.908
That's all.

1:56:02.172 --> 1:56:03.869
Sully just wants to sleep.

1:56:05.480 --> 1:56:06.568
Sleep it off.

1:56:08.004 --> 1:56:09.049
I said,

1:56:09.919 --> 1:56:13.749
stop calling yourself Sully.

1:56:13.792 --> 1:56:14.968
Shh!

1:56:28.764 --> 1:56:30.505
[breathing heavily]

1:56:31.593 --> 1:56:32.986
[screaming]

1:56:35.249 --> 1:56:36.685
[Lee grunting]

1:56:36.728 --> 1:56:38.165
[Sully yells]

1:56:41.777 --> 1:56:43.779
[ALL GRUNTING]

1:56:49.393 --> 1:56:51.787
[SULLY YELLING]

1:56:55.399 --> 1:56:57.140
[GROANS]

1:56:57.184 --> 1:56:58.924
Get off, Maren. Get off.

1:57:00.404 --> 1:57:02.406
-[Maren grunting]
-[Sully groaning]

1:57:09.631 --> 1:57:11.067
[Sully gasps deeply]

1:57:22.296 --> 1:57:23.862
[Maren gasping]

1:57:29.694 --> 1:57:30.956
[Lee grunting]

1:57:35.309 --> 1:57:36.223
[Lee] Careful.

1:57:37.137 --> 1:57:38.007
Come on.

1:57:38.051 --> 1:57:39.704
[panting and grunting]

1:57:44.535 --> 1:57:45.536
[sully groaning weakly]

1:57:51.455 --> 1:57:52.500
Up.

1:58:00.116 --> 1:58:01.683
[Sully groaning]

1:58:04.773 --> 1:58:06.383
[Sully wheezing]

1:58:08.429 --> 1:58:09.995
[panting]

1:58:12.346 --> 1:58:14.783
[screaming in pain]

1:58:17.438 --> 1:58:18.700
[gasping in pain]

1:58:21.485 --> 1:58:23.487
[gasping deeply]

1:58:32.540 --> 1:58:34.194
[Sully stops breathing]

1:58:46.684 --> 1:58:48.469
[panting]

1:58:55.302 --> 1:58:56.520
[panting]

1:59:45.526 --> 1:59:46.962
[continues panting]

1:59:48.703 --> 1:59:49.617
[grunting]

2:00:14.555 --> 2:00:16.992
[Lee] That's the man you met,
the one who followed you?

2:00:17.035 --> 2:00:18.733
I smelled him two blocks
from here.

2:00:18.776 --> 2:00:19.821
How the fuck did he find you?

2:00:21.257 --> 2:00:22.345
[Maren] Oh, no.

2:00:25.000 --> 2:00:26.349
[Lee coughing]

2:00:26.393 --> 2:00:27.481
[Lee gasping]

2:00:37.012 --> 2:00:38.709
[Lee coughing]

2:00:50.417 --> 2:00:51.287
[Maren] Hang on.

2:00:51.331 --> 2:00:52.419
[breathing nervously]

2:01:01.384 --> 2:01:03.647
Look. [whimpers]

2:01:03.691 --> 2:01:05.475
Fuck, he hit your lung.

2:01:05.519 --> 2:01:07.390
We gotta go to the ER.

2:01:07.434 --> 2:01:09.827
Air is coming out of this.
I can see it.

2:01:09.871 --> 2:01:10.741
He got Kayla.

2:01:12.047 --> 2:01:13.527
He got Kayla.

2:01:13.570 --> 2:01:15.311
Don't think about that
right now.

2:01:16.356 --> 2:01:17.966
[Lee] Fuck.

2:01:18.009 --> 2:01:20.795
[Maren] Lee, we can't handle
this by ourselves, and...

2:01:20.838 --> 2:01:22.187
-Am I bad?
-No.

2:01:22.231 --> 2:01:24.712
No, no, Lee.
You're good, all right?

2:01:24.755 --> 2:01:25.756
You're in shock.

2:01:27.541 --> 2:01:29.238
-Am I bad?
-No.

2:01:29.282 --> 2:01:30.718
No.

2:01:30.761 --> 2:01:33.329
We can't call
an ambulance, Lee.

2:01:33.373 --> 2:01:35.157
We can't let anybody in here.

2:01:35.766 --> 2:01:37.028
We're just gonna go.

2:01:37.812 --> 2:01:39.117
Come on.

2:01:39.161 --> 2:01:40.728
-I want you to eat first.
-Come on, Lee.

2:01:41.119 --> 2:01:42.120
Come on.

2:01:42.164 --> 2:01:43.861
-I want you to eat me.
-No.

2:01:43.905 --> 2:01:45.689
-I want you to eat...
-I'm not gonna eat him.

2:01:45.733 --> 2:01:47.430
-No. I want you to eat...
-I don't wanna.

2:01:47.474 --> 2:01:48.649
I want you to eat me.

2:01:48.692 --> 2:01:49.650
I want you to eat.

2:01:49.693 --> 2:01:51.086
-I want you to feed.
-No.

2:01:51.129 --> 2:01:52.783
-I want you to eat.
-No.

2:01:52.827 --> 2:01:54.655
-I don't wanna. I can't. Stop.
-I want you to do it, Maren.

2:01:54.698 --> 2:01:56.134
[Lee] I'm done here.
[Maren] No. No. No.

2:01:56.178 --> 2:01:58.267
-I want you to do it, Maren.
-Lee, stop.

2:01:58.311 --> 2:02:00.356
-No. No, I can't.
-Bones and all.

2:02:00.400 --> 2:02:01.749
-[Maren] I can't. Stop.
-[Lee coughs]

2:02:01.792 --> 2:02:03.054
[Lee] It's beautiful.
[Maren] No. No. Stop.

2:02:03.098 --> 2:02:04.969
Let me up. Let me up.
Let me up.

2:02:05.013 --> 2:02:06.536
[Lee] It's the easiest thing,
Maren, love.

2:02:06.580 --> 2:02:07.624
[Maren] No. No. No.

2:02:07.668 --> 2:02:09.104
[Lee] Just love me and eat.

2:02:12.455 --> 2:02:14.065
[imperceptible]
